## Phase 4: Dashboard Module
- [ ] 3D KPI cards (Total Products, Low Stock, Pending Receipts, Pending Deliveries, Transfers)
- [ ] Animated counters for KPI metrics
- [ ] Dynamic filter bar (document type, status, warehouse, category)
