## Phase 6: Operations Module
### 6a: Receipts (Incoming Stock)
- [ ] Receipts list with status filters
- [ ] Create receipt form (supplier, products, quantities)
- [ ] Validate receipt → auto-increment stock
- [ ] Status workflow: Draft → Waiting → Ready → Done

### 6b: Delivery Orders (Outgoing Stock)
- [ ] Delivery list with status filters
- [ ] Create delivery form (products, quantities, destination)
- [ ] Pick → Pack → Validate workflow → auto-decrement stock
- [ ] Status workflow: Draft → Waiting → Ready → Done

### 6c: Internal Transfers
- [ ] Transfer list
- [ ] Create transfer (source location → destination location)
- [ ] Validate → update location without changing total stock
- [ ] Log to move history

### 6d: Inventory Adjustments
- [ ] Adjustment list
- [ ] Select product + location, enter counted qty
- [ ] System calculates delta, logs adjustment
- [ ] Status workflow & validation

## Phase 7: Move History (Stock Ledger)
- [ ] Full ledger view with filters (product, location, date range, operation type)
- [ ] Animated timeline/log entries
- [ ] Export CSV functionality

## Phase 8: Settings Module
- [ ] Warehouse management (create, edit, activate/deactivate)
- [ ] Location management within warehouses
- [ ] My Profile page (edit name, avatar, password)

## Phase 9: State Management & Data Layer
